¡§Tui3 an2-ni Pi2-tek lau5 ti7 kaN-nih8; tok8-tok8 kau3-hoe7 thoe3 i chhiat-chhiat kiu5 Siong7-te3 ¡¨ (Su3-tou5 Heng7-toan7 12:5). Pi2-tek hou7 lang5 liah8 khi3 koaiN kaN, che si7 lang5 e5 khui3-lat8. Na7-si7 Seng3-keng koh kong2: ¡§Tok8-tok8 kau3-hoe7 thoe3 i chhiat-chhiat kiu5 Siong7-te3 ¡¨. Chhou-tai7 kau3-hoe7 chai-iaN2 tai7-to2 e5 leng5-lek8, kiat-ko2 Pi2-tek tit-tioh8 chu7-iu5. In-ui7 Siong7-te3 eng3-un2 kau3-hoe7 ki5-kiu5 e5 siaN, chhe thiN-sai3 lai5 kiu3 Pi2-tek chhut-kaN.
SiaN2-su7 lan2 bo5 beh tai7-to2? SiaN2-su7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 kau3-hoe7 bo5 sin3-kho3 tai7-to2 e5 hau7-ko2? Lan2 sou2 sun2-sit 5 hok-khi3 joa7 toa7 ah! Goan7 Siong7-te3 tui3 lan2 kong2-beng5, hou7 lan2 koh to3-tng2 kau3 chhou-tai7 kau3-hoe7 e5 si5-tai7, koh chit8 pai2 the2-giam7 tioh8 chit-e5 toa7 leng5-lek8 e5 bu2-khi3, chai i e5 kong-hau7, hou7 lan2 tui3 tai7-to2 choe3 chhiau chu7-jian5 e5 kang.
Choe3-ko E5 Chui2-chun2.
Tai7-to2 si7 siok8-leng5 keng-giam7 choe3-ko e5 chui2-chun2. U7 chin choe7 sin3-tou5 teh khoa-khau2 in sou2 tit-tioh8 chhiau-oat8 chu7-jian5 e5 the2-giam7, chong2-si7 in bo5 ti3-i3 tai7-to2 e5 su7. U7 lang5 sui-jian5 tit-tioh8 Seng3 Sin5 tek8-piat8 e5 un-su3, chong2-si7 bo5 it-teng7 choe3 tai7-to2 e5 lang5 . Ti7 tai7-to2 e5 si7 sit-pai7 e5 lang5 , chiu7 ti7 tak8 hong-bin7 long2 oe7 sit-pai7. Na7-si7 tui3 tai7-to2 kap Ki-tok kau-poe5, chiu7-si7 tit-tioh8 te7-it toa7 e5 hok-khi3.
Li2 siok8-leng5 e5 theng5-tou7, choat8-tui3 boe7 pi2 tai7-to2 e5 seng-oah8 khah koan5. Ia5-sou Ki-tok chiuN7 thiN che7 ti7 Pe7 Siong7-te3 e5 toa7-peng5, si7 beh ui7-tioh8 I e5 kau3-hoe7 tam-tng tai7-to2 e5 toa7 kang-chok. 1900 goa7 ni5 i2-lai5, I iu5-goan5 an2-ni teh thoe3 lan2 ki5-to2. I khoaN3 tai7-to2 si7 I sou2 tioh8 choe3 te7-it iau3-kin2 e5 kang, sou2-i2 tai7-to2 chiu7-si7 kap I saN-kap che7 ti7 po2-cho7 e5 seng-oah8, si7 leng5-seng3 choe3-ko e5 chui2-chun2. U7-hun7 ti7 tai7-to2 e5 kang-chok, chiu7-si7 toa3 ti7 toe7-chiuN7 teh choe3 Chu2 Ia5-sou ti7 thiN-teng2 sou2 teh choe3 kang7-khoan2 e5 kang. ¡§In-ui7 I tng5-tng5 oah8, lai5 thoe3 in ki5-kiu5¡¨ (Hi-pek-lai5 7:25).
HiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, kiam2-chhai2 li2 teh tui-kiu5 tek8-piat8 e5 un-su3, ai3 tit-tioh8 bo5 peng5-siong5 e5 hian2-hian7, chiu7-si7 li2 sou2 ai3, kam2-cheng5-tek e5 toa7 keng-giam7. Kiam2-chhai2 li2 khoaN3-khin hiah-e5 iau2-be7 tit-tioh8 e5 lang5 , li2 liah8-choe3 ti7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 sin3-giong2 the2-giam7, li2 e5 leng5-seng3 pi2 in khah koan5. Na7-si7 goa2 beh ka7 li2 kong2, choat8-tui3 m7 si7; leng5-seng3 choe3-ko e5 ki3-ho7, chiu7-si7 tai7-to2 e5 seng-oah8. Li2 na7 bo5 kau3 chia, li2 chiu7-si7 iau2 put-chiok, koh chha chin hng7. Bo5-lun7 li2 joa7-nih kiong5-tiau koh khoa-khau2 li2 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 keng-giam7, a2-si7 tit-tioh8 tek8-piat8 e5 un-su3, li2 na7 m7-chai beh chaiN2-iuN7 thoe3 pat8-lang5 ki5-to2, li2 ui7-tioh8 Chu2 sou2 choe3 e5 kang chiu7 bo5 leng5-lek8, li2 e5 un-su3 ia7 bo5 ke3-tat8. Sou2-i2 tai7-to2 e5 seng-oah8, chiu7-si7 kap Chu2 Ia5-sou saN-kap che7 po2-cho7 e5 seng-oah8, che si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 khoaN3-tang7 e5 kang.
