Tai7-to2 chiu7-si7 beh hou7 Seng3 Sin5 tui3 teng2-bin7 koan3-ak toa7 koan5-leng5 e5 kang-chok. Na7 bo5 lang5 saN thoe3 ki5-to2, chiu7 m7-bat u7 hun3-heng. Li2 khi3 chha5-kho2 ke3-khi3 toa7 hun3-heng e5 ki3-liok8, chiu7 oe7 chai hit-e5 pi3-koat kap goan5-in chiu7-si7 ki5-to2. Siong7-te3 kam2-tong7 chit8-kun5 e5 sin3-tou5 ti7-chia, ti7-hia, u7-si5 nng7, saN lang5 na7-tiaN7, chong2-si7 in choan5-bu7 ki5-to2, hit-e5 kiat-ko2 chiu7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 toa7-toa7 koan3-ak.
